This auction is for a CMP Winchester Service Grade M1 Garand, which I purchased 3 years ago from the CMP. Service Grade is the highest of the non premium CMP grades and Winchester service grades are no longer available from the CMP (and were priced higher than Springfield or HRA Service Grades when they were available). This rifle is not coated in cosmoline like many of the CMP rifles and should be easy to easy to make ready for the range.
